external_knowledge:
Points scored: Reflects the performance in a single match; Max points indicate the highest achieved in a game; 
Average NRR: This is the average net run rate calculated for the team across matches, reflecting consistency in performance;
Coach: Often referred to as the strategic leader of the team;
Recent Matches: Refers to matches that are the most recent in a team's history, aiding in evaluating current form.

sql:
SELECT team_id, team_name, team_location
FROM teams
WHERE team_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT team_id FROM matches);

SELECT teams.team_name, coaches.coach_name
FROM teams
LEFT JOIN coaches ON teams.coach_id = coaches.coach_id;
